ud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-5.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: MachineGames/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe chest you’ll be opening is in the room on the right. Over on the left, you’ll find a room with a bunch of radio equipment and two notes — a \u003cstrong\u003eCloud Status Logbook\u003c/strong\u003e and a \u003cstrong\u003eCloud Atlas Page\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe logbook lists a series of times and types of clouds. The atlas page has the types of clouds associated with numbers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"cloud-atlas-chest-code-solution\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e‘Cloud Atlas\u003c/strong\u003e’ chest code solution\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1622\" data-pswp-width=\"2880\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Indiana Jones and the Great Circle Cloud Atlas logbook\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-4.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: MachineGames/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo find the code, you have to take the handwritten times at the bottom of the Cloud Atlas Page, and reference them against the Cloud Status Logbook to find what types of clouds you’re looking for. The times are \u003cstrong\u003e13\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e9\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e16\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e14 \u003c/strong\u003e(ignoring the 10 after because it doesn’t matter).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1622\" data-pswp-width=\"2880\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Indiana Jones and the Great Circle Cloud Atlas Page\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/12/Indiana-Jones-and-the-Great-Circle-Cloud-Atlas-3.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: MachineGames/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn the Cloud Status Logbook page, these times have \u003cstrong\u003eCirrus\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eStratus\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eCirrus\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eCumulonimbus\u003c/strong\u003e observed. Back on the Cloud Atlas Page, these become the code for the chest in the other room — \u003cstrong\u003e0609\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOpen the chest to find some cash and the \u003cstrong\u003eGizeh Medicine exploration book\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor more \u003cem\u003eIndiana Jones and the Great Circle\u003c/em\u003e guides, here’s where to find the “\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/e/494017\"\u003eBright Future\u003c/a\u003e” chest code.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSee More:\u003cspan\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/guides\"\u003eGuides\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/indiana-jones-great-circle-guide\"\u003eIndiana Jones and the Great Circle guides\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/pc\"\u003ePC\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/playstation\"\u003ePlayStation\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/xbox\"\u003eXbox\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/indiana-jones-and-the-great-circle/441964\"\u003eIndiana Jones and the Great Circle\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
